
✱ SessionFactory
    - Create session, connect to database by Hibernate Configuration file.
    - Each database has 1 session factory.
    - Create Sesson object (by call the openSession method)

✱ Session
    - Created by SessionFactory
    - Each Session is like 1 connection to DB
    - in Hibernate, Session is use for save and retrieve persistent objects (persistent objects = entity)
    - Main function: do operations (such as: Create, read, delete) for instances of mapped entity classes

✱ Persistence
    - This class contain static methods to obtain EntityManagerFactory instance.

✱ Query
    - This interface is implemented by each JPA vendor to obtain relational objects that meet the criteria.